Package: netspot
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A simple IDS with statistical learning
 NetSpot flags network anomalies in real-time. It monitors
 network statistics (time series) and detect when some rare 
 event occurs (peaks).
